{"tid":1480793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[818維園]「五大訴求」「光復香港 時代革命」為口號","createTime":"2019-08-17T12:39:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T05:00:51.000Z","uid":4154,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"52978a88af30cc6bcad87b5c48f665db03dd8a5d","tid":1480793,"uid":4154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:39:26.000Z","msg":"每次遊行集會<br />\n都聽到唔少人嗌「香港人加油」同「林鄭下台」<br />\n<br />\n首先我同意香港人要加油<br />\n呢個口號可以鼓舞士氣<br />\n不過大家企出嚟最主要目的<br />\n係要向林鄭政權同埋各媒體表達我哋所爭取嘅嘢<br />\n所以我哋要大聲講出五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n其次林鄭下台大家可能會開心<br />\n但佢下台又點？<br />\n冇雙普選機制下<br />\n下任特首咪又係689 2.0 或者 777 2.0<br />\n同樣係中共傀儡做特首<br />\n比起林鄭下台<br />\n雙普選先係更加值得我哋爭取嘅事<br />\n而雙普選正正係我哋五大訴求之一<br />\n<br />\n喺度向大家重申五大訴求<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一：撤回惡法<br />\n二：收回暴動定義<br />\n三：撤銷所有示威者控罪<br />\n四：徹底追究警隊濫權<br />\n五：實行雙普選</span></span><br />\n<br />\n至於「光復香港 時代革命」<br />\n我想借用攬炒巴嘅言詞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t6423Ox.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft6423Ox.png&h=e60f3204&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論如何<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">818 維園見<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZZXTq2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZZXTq2e.jpg&h=e000def0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qGjnjnf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqGjnjnf.jpg&h=66072ffc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xNvmzVB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxNvmzVB.jpg&h=104f93a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XJ11zVC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXJ11zVC.jpg&h=e76790ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/swgAEni.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FswgAEni.jpg&h=6cad3670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UzJZ52i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUzJZ52i.jpg&h=7741cb03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41d857724eb377842c2b864cd618f50f8165ae24","tid":1480793,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:40:31.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2e7aba0d9032c19eaa847a785d696098b787e818","tid":1480793,"uid":4154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:42:39.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"0559fdc896660e9b917886d760a5376b5ac89e2b","tid":1480793,"uid":282280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:43:37.000Z","msg":"因果由國，容港治己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc706ef046247c26f8be572ab14c6f1bfc5a4aa6","tid":1480793,"uid":4154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:43:42.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"9937a666aa228a8d76a03143a8d4860bd54ec308","tid":1480793,"uid":4154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:43:53.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"85f16fd9be23ac10080a890aef7ede8b29f9a251","tid":1480793,"uid":4154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:44:09.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"fde2f5c5962fd93997dcbbd911559393d1a23713","tid":1480793,"uid":4154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:44:40.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"6dde26b1b6f7f408703b6c62dc5321ad1b45681d","tid":1480793,"uid":283738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:45:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3043939a32baaaa6a8a3395d36b56875d44deaf","tid":1480793,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:45:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19ec8ef130857c5b8438e6063dccf7